==制作==
2018年9月报道，[[妮可·基德曼|妮可·基德曼]]和[[雷夫·范恩斯|雷夫·范恩斯]]正在谈判出演该片<ref>{{Cite web|title=Nicole Kidman could star in new film about Sutton Hoo|url=https://www.eadt.co.uk/news/suffolk-sutton-hoo-film-will-nicole-kidman-star-2502656|access-date=2022-01-14|date=2018-09-21|last=Townsend|first=Emily|work=East Anglian Daily Times|language=en-GB}}</ref>。然而到了2019年8月，基德曼不再参与该项目，[[嘉莉·慕萊根|嘉莉·慕萊根]]出演代替她。影片的版权也从[[BBC電影|BBC電影]]转移到了[[Netflix|Netflix]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Carey Mulligan to Star in Netflix Drama ‘The Dig’ (Exclusive)|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/general-news/carey-mulligan-star-netflix-drama-dig-1235550/|access-date=2022-01-14|date=2019-08-29|last=Galuppo|first=Mia|work=[[荷里活報道|The Hollywood Reporter]]|language=en-US}}</ref> 。[[莉莉·詹姆斯|莉莉·詹姆斯]]在9月进入谈判，加入演员阵容<ref>{{Cite web|title=Lily James to Join Carey Mulligan in Netflix Period Drama ‘Dig’ (Exclusive)|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/lily-james-join-carey-mulligan-netflix-movie-dig-1236981/|access-date=2022-01-14|date=2019-09-05|last=Kit|first=Borys|work=The Hollywood Reporter|language=en-US}}</ref>。2019年10月，{{le|约翰尼·弗林|Johnny Flynn (musician)}}、{{le|本·卓别林|Ben Chaplin}}、{{le|肯·斯托特|Ken Stott}}和{{le|莫妮卡·多兰|Monica Dolan}}加入了该片的演员阵容<ref>{{Cite web|title=‘The Dig’: Johnny Flynn, Ben Chaplin, Ken Stott & Monica Dolan Join Carey Mulligan, Ralph Fiennes & Lily James In Netflix Pic Now Underway In UK|url=https://deadline.com/2019/10/the-dig-johnny-flynn-ben-chaplin-ken-stott-monica-dolan-join-carey-mulligan-ralph-fiennes-lily-james-in-netflix-pic-now-underway-in-uk-1202754951/|access-date=2022-01-14|date=2019-10-08|last=Wiseman|first=Andreas|work=Deadline|language=en-US}}</ref>。

2019年10月开始在英国萨里郡的沙克尔福德进行[[主体拍摄|主体拍摄]]，外景拍摄在萨福克郡的遗址发现地附近进行<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Dig to film in the UK|url=https://www.theknowledgeonline.com/the-knowledge-bulletin/post/2019/07/26/the-dig-to-film-in-the-uk-in-early-september-|access-date=2022-01-14|work=The Knowledge|language=en}}</ref>。

